    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_386558">I don't think &quot;lag&quot; is the reason people are leaving vanguard.  The vast majority of players can deal with lag. most can deal with a broken quest, or ability or whatever. <br />
<br />
Getting disconnected from groups, losing the chat server, random kicks to the desktop, no end game content, no reason/purpose to pvp..<br />
<br />
these are the things that are causing the majority to leave. imo.</div>
