    <!-- message -->
    <div align="left" id="post_message_386845">The end of the questline in Harbor of Tahatamani or whoever its spelled requires at least 2 groups and medals there do too. You should have seen how horrid the lag was with just 2 groups when we did it. I can only imagine the horror of 4.<br />
<br />
I got 2 gig of fast ddr2 ram, an AMD duel core 2.4 cpu, and a 512mb geforce 7950 GT. And in most of those temples with 2 groups I was getting 15-20 fps. People with lesser systems said it was basically a slide show for them and they could barely use their abilities and spells.</div>
    <!-- / message -->
    
    
